General Information

Green Lipped Mussel New Zealand - 250s

Warnings

Do not take if allergic to seafood. Always read the label. Take only as directed. If taking prescription medication or if in doubt, talk to your health professional. Contains: Shellfish and sulfites.

Common Uses

This formula contains 100% pure New Zealand Green Lipped Mussel powder, sustainably sourced from Green Lipped Mussels from the clean, clear waters of New Zealand. This formula: Contains 100% New Zealand sustainably sourced Green Lipped Mussel powder Contains Green Lipped Mussel which naturally provide a source of protein and fat

Ingredients

INGREDIENTS: Each capsule contains: Mussel powder 500 mg, equiv. to fresh Green lipped mussel 2.5 g Green lipped mussel powder (83.9%), Gelatin, Purified water, Sodium Lauryl Sulphate

Directions

SERVING SUGGESTION: Take 1-3 capsules daily, best taken with food.
